{"tid":12712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐LiHKG]但其實大家互相鼓勵真係好柒","createTime":"2016-11-29T18:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T19:36:10.000Z","uid":3373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faf7f7578d8fe3556a5f44c7e068fb1f0b843ff0","tid":12712,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:48:03.000Z","msg":"個討論區開左幾日，每次上黎都話大家要振作，要死守，情況不容樂觀乜乜物物。<br />\n<br />\n屌你醒下啦，無野搵野驚，老定啲啦<br />\n我上黎係想吹水，上親黎都係呢啲post，個感覺好似係佔中聽到今天我咁，好撚柒。<br />\n<br />\n唔想LiHKG只係個潮流，就一切歸於正常，開po又好回po又好，用番平常心，死谷人氣只會令人覺得呢度無料到。有麝自然香，浸下浸下就出到LiHKG獨有既文化，到時自自然然就吸引到人。"},{"pid":"fa50af223c296ecb53e40f927282ee1a11b41b0e","tid":12712,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"332ec6bc9a1b9c44f44a861efea3af72d3b0809b","tid":12712,"uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f328d25ac09730420575c16698e6e6a51c16adb","tid":12712,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:55:07.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"840364bb6415006272404cbc4b2e9c3fc99278c0","tid":12712,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:55:40.000Z","msg":"已刪高登app返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be35481d7ff2142a87ae67cddc975b02cda56fba","tid":12712,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:58:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8497f3ed6fe47aa2faa5f3f14003bcbfcac43f31","tid":12712,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:59:52.000Z","msg":"已被bam返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"333a7d402814625bc531a39a69139acd0d98f136","tid":12712,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:00:42.000Z","msg":"Agger 用平常心咪得"},{"pid":"2d37f4bc3673ea4dac01331c940a597f5a3bef86","tid":12712,"uid":29605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29